      "title": "Presidential swearing-in tomorrow - at the Parliament Complex",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe will be sworn in as the 8th Executive President of Sri Lanka tomorrow (21st) morning at the Parliament Complex.",
        "Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe asked the Speaker to take the oath of office at the Parliament complex."
      ],
